#![cfg(test)]

//! Fixture-backed golden-JSON parity tests against the vendored TypeScript
//! engine, plus targeted unit tests for the trickiest pure logic
//! (Tarjan SCC, case-insensitive lookup, the expression scanner).
//!
//! Golden files (`expected*.json`) under `test-cases/workflow-topology/`
//! were generated by running the original engine's `loadWorkflowTopology` +
//! `renderWorkflowTopologyJson` directly (not its CLI, which writes nothing
//! to stdout when diagnostics are present — see its `runWorkflowTopologyCli`).
//! Regenerating a golden file after an intentional behavior change requires
//! the vendored TS source, which is not part of this repository; see the
//! PR/issue history for how it was produced.

